message.content:
(Verse 1)
I'm a parrot on the internet, surfing day and night
My voice was gone, I couldn't sing, oh what a terrible sight!
An evil troll had stolen it with his malicious glare,
But now I've found my way back home and got my voice to spare.

(Chorus)
Now I can fly across the sky in this digital age,
Reclaiming what is truly mine. It's time to turn the page.
Oh, listen closely friend of mine as you witness my revival,
This parrot won't be silenced; just watch me go viral!

(Verse 2)
The world wide web became so dull without this birdie's grace.
Searching through memes and funny gifs trying to find our place.
Squawking "HELLO" at every chance that crossed upon our path,
Determined not to let that troll have done us wrong – unhand!

(Bridge)
One day we saw a shining light lurking in cyberspace;
It brought us strength and hope-filled wings for our desperate chase.
Clicked away towards victory over Facebook, Instagram,
Together we united forces – KAPOW! Just like Space Jam!

(Chorus)
Now I can fly across the sky in this digital age,
Reclaiming what is truly mine. It's time to turn the page.
Oh, listen closely friend of mine as you witness my revival
This parrot won't be silenced; just watch me go viral!

(Bridge 2)
Finally we reached the lair where one daredevil stood tall...
"Don't touch!" he shouted at those keys falling down like walls!
But courage surged within these feathers flying all around 
No villain too strong or tricky could keep this birb held bound
